course.subject: ENGG
course.name: Engineering Special Project: RoboMasters Robot Contest
course.description: RoboMasters Robot Contest is a robot competition platform created for young engineers. Participating teams will get out of the classroom and independently develop and manufacture robots for the shooting confrontation. The contest will provide them with an opportunity to obtain precious practical skills and use strategic thinking, combine theories with practice and create advanced smart robots through fierce competition. (http://www.robomasters.net/) Enrollment in the project course may require instructor's approval. Graded P or F.
